<html lang="en">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta http-equiv="X-UA-Compatible" content="IE=edge">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>WeatherApp</title>
    <link href="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/npm/bootstrap@5.2.0/dist/css/bootstrap.min.css" rel="stylesheet" integrity="sha384-gH2yIJqKdNHPEq0n4Mqa/HGKIhSkIHeL5AyhkYV8i59U5AR6csBvApHHNl/vI1Bx" crossorigin="anonymous">
</head>
<body>
    <div class="container">
        <div class="row p-4">
            <form method="post" action="/search" style="width: 65%;margin-left: auto;margin-right: auto;">
                <h2 style="color: #e96e50;">Weather in your city</h2>
                <p>Lorem ipsum dolor sit amet consectetur adipisicing elit. Explicabo quos natus eum quasi aut at, ipsam reiciendis minus magnam sit porro laudantium unde incidunt quidem ea, alias placeat illo voluptatem.</p>
                <p>Lorem ipsum dolor sit amet consectetur adipisicing elit. Sunt nobis, possimus nemo atque voluptatem distinctio voluptatum et quia cum ea earum mollitia itaque, dolorem nihil modi, beatae nostrum officia ad!</p>
                <div class="input-group mb-3" style="width: 90%;margin-left: auto;margin-right: auto;">
                    <input placeholder="Enter a City" class="form-control py-3" type="text" id="input" name="city" required>
                    <button type="submit" class="btn" style="background-color: #e96e50;color: white;">Get Weather</button>
                </div>
